<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA13">
<l>paṭivaṭṭat tāmarai paṇṭulaka nīrēṟ</l>
<l>ṟaṭivaṭṭat tālaḷappa nīṇṭa – muṭivaṭṭa</l>
<l>mākāya mūṭaṟut taṇṭampōy nīṇṭatē</l>
<l>mākāya māyniṉṟa māṟku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While once in a circle he measured with [his] foot the lotus that is</l>
<l>the circle of the earth, receiving the world with water, the tall circle</l>
<l>of [his] crown cut into the middle of space [and] extended</l>
<l>up to the [top of the world] egg, [the crown] of Māl who stood as a great body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
